{"title_page": "My Giant Life", "text_new": "{{Infobox television\n| show_name            = My Giant Life\n| image                = My Giant Life logo tlc.png\n| caption              = \n| show_name_2          = \n| genre                = [[Reality television]]\n| creator              = \n| starring             = {{Plainlist|\n* Colleen \"Coco\" Smith\n* Haleigh Hampton\n* Nancy Mulkey\n* [[Lindsay Kay Hayward]]\n* Katja Bavendam\n* Alicia Jay\n\n}}\n| opentheme            = \n| country              = United States\n| language             = English\n| num_seasons          = 3\n| num_episodes         = 22\n| list_episodes        = \n| executive_producer   = \n| runtime              = 42 minutes\n| company              = Workaholic Productions\n| channel              = [[TLC (TV channel)|TLC]]\n| picture_format       = [[480i]] ([[Standard-definition television|SDTV]])<br/>[[1080i]] ([[High-definition television|HDTV]])\n| first_aired          = July 14, 2015\n| last_aired           = November 5, 2017\n| related              = \n| website              = http://www.tlc.com/tv-shows/my-giant-life/\n}}\n\n'''''My Giant Life''''' is an American [[reality television]] series that premiered on the [[TLC (TV channel)|TLC]] cable network, on July 14, 2015. Season 1 of the series revolved around 4 women who are taller than 6 feet 6 inches (198&nbsp;cm).<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thewrap.com/tlcs-my-giant-life-follows-6-foot-9-woman-while-grocery-shopping-in-new-clip-exclusive-video/|title=\nTLC\u2019s \u2018My Giant Life\u2019 Follows 6-Foot-9 Woman While Grocery Shopping in New Clip (Exclusive Video)|accessdate=January 4, 2016|date=July 14, 2015|first=Kathy|last=Zerbib|publisher=[[TheWrap]]}}</ref> Season 2 follows three of the four women from the first season, with Nancy Mulkey replaced by a new woman, 6&nbsp;ft 9 in (206&nbsp;cm) German-born New Yorker Katya, and her 5&nbsp;ft 2 in (157&nbsp;cm) American wife.\n\n==Series overview==\n{{Series overview\n| color1       = 