|title=Semakan Penerima Darjah Kebesaran, Bintang dan Pingat|publisher=[[Prime Minister's Department (Malaysia)]]}}</ref>\n\n* {{Flag|Malacca}} :\n** [[File:MY-MAL Exalted Order of Malacca.svg|50px]] Grand Commander of the [[List of post-nominal letters (Malacca)|Order of Malacca]] (DGSM) - '''Datuk Seri''' (2015)<ref name=\":1\" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2015/10/10/dr-wee-gets-malacca-award-mustapa-receives-dgsm-title/|publisher=[[The Star (Malaysia)|The Star]]|date=10 October 2015|accessdate=11 September 2018|title=Dr Wee gets Malacca award}}</ref>\n* {{Flag|Pahang}} :\n** [[File:MY-PAH Order of the Crown of Pahang - Grand Knight - SIMP.svg|50px]] Grand Knight of the [[Orders, decorations, and medals of Pahang|Order of the Crown of Pahang]] (SIMP) - '''Dato'''' (1998)<ref name=\":1\" />\n** [[File:MY-PAH Order of Sultan Ahmad Shah of Pahang - Grand Knight - SSAP.svg|50px]] Grand Knight of the [[Orders, decorations, and medals of Pahang|Order of Sultan Ahmad Shah of Pahang]] (SSAP) - '''Dato' Sri''' (2008)<ref name=\":1\" />\n* {{Flag|Selangor}} :\n** [[File:MY-SEL Order of the Crown of Selangor - Knight Commander - DPMS.svg|50px]] Knight Commander of the [[Order of the Crown of Selangor#Knight Commander|Order of the Crown of Selangor]] (DPMS) - '''Dato'''' (1994)<ref name=\":1\" />\n\n==See also==\n{{portal|Malaysia}}\n*[[Budget Select Committee (Malaysia)]]\n*[[Jeli (federal constituency)]]\n*[[Air Lanas (state constituency)]]\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{commons category|Mustapa Mohamed}}\n\n{{Kelantan-FedRep}}\n{{Fifth Mahathir cabinet}}\n{{Second Abdullah cabinet}}\n{{Third Abdullah cabinet}}\n{{First Najib cabinet}}\n{{Second Najib cabinet}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Mustapa Mohamed}}\n[[Category:1950 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Kelantan]]\n[[Category:Malaysian people of Malay descent]]\n[[Category:Malaysian Muslims]]\n[[Category:Malaysian economists]]\n[[Category:Malay