ral constituency)]]\n*[[Air Lanas (state constituency)]]\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{commons category|Mustapa Mohamed}}\n\n{{Kelantan-FedRep}}\n{{Fifth Mahathir cabinet}}\n{{Second Abdullah cabinet}}\n{{Third Abdullah cabinet}}\n{{First Najib cabinet}}\n{{Second Najib cabinet}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Mustapa Mohamed}}\n[[Category:1950 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Kelantan]]\n[[Category:Malaysian people of Malay descent]]\n[[Category:Malaysian Muslims]]\n[[Category:Malaysian economists]]\n[[Category:Malaysian United Indigenous Party politicians]]\n[[Category:United Malays National Organisation politicians]]\n[[Category:Members of the Dewan Rakyat]]\n[[Category:Members of the Dewan Negara]]\n[[Category:Members of the Kelantan State Legislative Assembly]]\n[[Category:Government ministers of Malaysia]]\n[[Category:Agriculture ministers of Malaysia]]\n[[Category:Education ministers of Malaysia]]\n[[Category:Finance ministers of Malaysia]]\n[[Category:University of Melbourne alumni]]\n[[Category:Boston University alumni]]\n[[Category:21st-century Malaysian politicians]]\n[[Category:21st-century Malaysian people]]\n", "name_user": "NCTb", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eElection results", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mustapa_Mohamed"}
{"title_page": "A1 Top Masta", "text_new": "{{Multiple issues|\n{{notability|music|date=April 2020}}\n{{tone|date=April 2020}}\n{{too much detail|date=April 2020}}\n{{Cleanup rewrite|riddled with peacock terms, vague expressions, grammar and syntax errors, etc|article|date=April 2020}}\n{{Refimprove|date=April 2020}}\n{{Orphan|date=April 2020}}\n}}\n\n'''A1 Top Masta''' (\u9876\u7ea7\u73a9\u5bb6) (ATM) is a Chinese [[hip-hop]] group from [[Chengdu]] founded in 2017, consisting of three members: AnsrJ (\u5218\u9759\u5b81),<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://open.spotify.com/artist/6LUarizJpinCjQ7VBpbpjd|title=Ansrj|website=Spotify|language=en|access-date=2020-04-04}}</ref> Lil Shin (\u674e\u5c14\u65b0) and Mengzi (\u5b5f\u5b50).<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://open.spotify.com/artist/4RNIsIsoiSbSAWapBf9q0w|title=Mengzi|website=Spotify|language=en|access-date=2020-04-04}}</ref> They are the members of C.D.C (Chengdu Rap House), and they are good friends with [[Higher Brothers]]. The group is good at combining [[Sichuanese dialects]] with [[Mandarin Chinese|Mandarin]], and it is known for the first album: \u9876\u7ea7\u73a9\u5bb6 (ding ji wan jia).<ref name=\"163com\">{{Cite web|url=https://music.163.com/|title=\u7f51\u6613\u4e91\u97f3\u4e50|website=\u7f51\u6613\u4e91\u97f3\u4e50|access-date=2020-04-04}}</ref> These three maintain a high level of technical creativity, and the album is mainly in hip-hop style. The production of this album is all made by themselves including lyrics, composing, recording and mixing. The title song \"Double\"<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=djqXsjy8hz0|title=Double|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref> is composed by these three people, and is arranged by S-kiddi, an excellent Chinese producer. The songs express the special melody and rhythm, performing an extraordinary effect. Twelve tracks from the album and one bonus track, combining local and overseas cultures, the high and lows are obviously like a roller coaster to bring a new experience to the listener, which interprets the new level of hip-hop in China.\n\n==History==\nAnsr J released his first single \"School Uniform is not fashion\"<ref>{{Citation|title=\u6821\u670d\u4e0d\u6f6e\u3010Mixtape\u8bd5\u542c\u3011 - AnsrJ|url=https://streetvoice.com/answerj/songs/74248/|language=zh-Hant|access-date=2020-04-04}}</ref> (\u6821\u670d\u4e0d\u6f6e) as early as 2009, when he was a high school student. Taking the school uniform as the topic, although the content is not related to the school uniform, it is enough to attract people to listen to it.\u00a0 This single has a great influence in the local student circle in Chengdu. Every student has this song in the MP3, which can be said to be the youth of many people. Later in 2013, Ansr J focused more on running his own clothing brand Johnny Designs, and music was left behind. In 2016, the single \"Renmin South Road\"(\u4eba\u6c11\u5357\u8def)<ref name=\"163com\"/> was released, and it is another popular song after \"School Uniform is not fashion\". Then many classic singles and Mixtape \"FNTE\"<ref name=\"163com\"/> was released, FNTE's full spell is \"from nothing to everything\", from nothing to everything , AnsrJ did indeed rely on himself from scratch, step by step to the present.\n\nLil Shin is also the \"old guy\" of Chengdu Rap House, one of the founding members of C.D.C. As early as the end of BigZoo in 2010, Chengdu Rap entered the Cypher in the C.D.C era, and there was Lil Shin. Lil Shin\u2019s current job is as a director, and he also commutes from 9 to 5 while doing rap. The director's work also made him handy in MV editing, which is also a special skill that other Rapper does not have. One of the Lil Shin's most widely circulated works is \"Intoo\"<ref name=\"163com\"/> included in \"No. 901\",<ref name=\"163com\"/> which is a gentle and delicate love song that favors popular style. This song is adapted from [[Sam Smith]]'s classic single \"I'm Not The Only One<ref>{{Citation|title=I'm Not The Only One|url=https://open.spotify.com/track/7795WJLVKJoAyVoOtCWqXN|language=en|access-date=2020-04-04}}</ref>\", which uses the original song as a hook part, and adds a low rap, and illustrates Chengdu dialect is not only suitable for trap, it is also very tender to sing love songs.\n\nAnother member, Mengzi, was also one of the earliest members of the Chengdu rap club. In 2011, he formed the Onstyle combination with Lil Shin, which is also the first combination of the rap club. But Onstyle currently does not have many songs on the platform. Mengzi left the team for almost two years for some reasons and was unable to participate in the team's song.\n\n==Group Members==\nThese are Chinese names; surnames appear first.\n\n* Ansr J\uff08\u5218\u9759\u5b81\uff09from Chengdu\n* Lil Shin\uff08\u674e\u5c14\u65b0\uff09from Chengdu\n* Mengzi\uff08\u5b5f\u5b50\uff09from Chengdu\n\n==Discography==\n'''First album: Ding ji Wan Jia (\u9876\u7ea7\u73a9\u5bb6)'''<ref name=\"163com\"/>\n\nThe group released the first album: Ding Ji Wan Jia in 2018. It consists 12 tracks and one bonus track called \"Food & Liquor\"<ref name=\"163com\"/> which were made by themselves including lyrics, composing, recording and mixing.\n\n'''Second album: 1Fan!LP (\u4e00\u756a!LP)'''<ref name=\"163com\"/>\n\nIn the same year, they dropped their second album: 1Fan!LP, compared to the last album, the track has increased to 13. In terms of creation, the top three players have made new breakthroughs. The genre is wider than the first album. Here, \"1fan!\" is regarded as top-level meaning, and can also be read as \"Awesome!\"\n\n'''The latest album: Hi Business (\u55e8\u751f\u610f)'''<ref name=\"163com\"/>\n\nThis album contains eight newly created songs, which can be said to be a hard and soft album. In addition to new trap, electronic and rock, there are soft love songs and R&B parts. The single \"Hi business\" pays homage to [[Run-DMC]]. This single is full of skills and strong rhythms; \"Get it done\"<ref name=\"163com\"/> is the most breakthrough single. In this single, Ansrj combines rock's energy and the powerful rap which is perfectly embodies the top player spirit of A.T.M.; the single \"color\",<ref name=\"163com\"/> produced by producer G23, is a typical new trap. In the song, Mengzi's flow is quite prominent, which can be called textbook level flow. It is worth mentioning that the single \"friends\",<ref name=\"163com\"/> in which the comfortable melody of Lil shin shows the all-around rap talent of A.T.M.\n\nA.T.M., who just finished touring in 2019, released the album at the end of the year, and will continue to release their second official album next year. The changeable music style and breakthrough of have laid an all-around stage for them and laid a perfect foundation for their debut next year.\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Chinese hip hop musicians]]\n", "text_old": "{{Multiple issues|\n{{notability|music|date=April 2020}}\n{{tone|date=April 2020}}\n{{too much detail|date=April 2020}}\n{{Cleanup rewrite|riddled with peacock terms, vague expressions, grammar and syntax errors, etc|article|date=April 2020}}\n{{Refimprove|date=April 2020}}\n{{Orphan|date=April 2020}}\n}}\n\n'''A1 Top Masta''' (\u9876\u7ea7\u73a9\u5bb6) (ATM) is a Chinese [[hip-hop]] group from [[Chengdu]] founded in 2017, consisting of three members: AnsrJ (\u5218\u9759\u5b81),<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://open.spotify.com/artist/6LUarizJpinCjQ7VBpbpjd|title=Ansrj|website=Spotify|language=en|access-date=2020-04-04}}</ref> Lil Shin (\u674e\u5c14\u65b0) and Mengzi (\u5b5f\u5b50).<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://open.spotify.com/artist/4RNIsIsoiSbSAWapBf9q0w|title=Mengzi|website=Spotify|language=en|access-date=2020-04-04}}</ref> They are the members of C.D.C (Chengdu Rap House), and they are good friends with [[Higher Brothers]]. The group is good at combining [[Sichuanese dialects]] with [[Mandarin Chinese|Mandarin]], and it is known for the first album: \u9876\u7ea7\u73a9\u5bb6 (ding ji wan jia).<ref name=\"163com>{{Cite web|url=https://music.163.com/|title=\u7f51\u6613\u4e91\u97f3\u4e50|website=\u7f51\u6613\u4e91\u97f3\u4e50|access-date=2020-04-04}}</ref> These three maintain a high level of technical creativity, and the album is mainly in hip-hop style. The production of this album is all made by themselves including lyrics, composing, recording and mixing. The title song \"Double\"<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=djqXsjy8hz0|title=Double|last=|first=|date=|website=|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref> is composed by these three people, and is arranged by S-kiddi, an excellent Chinese producer. The songs express the special melody and rhythm, performing an extraordinary effect. Twelve tracks from the album and one bonus track, combining local and overseas cultures, the high and lows are obviously like a roller coaster to bring a new experience to the listener, which interprets the new level of hip-hop in China.\n\n==History==\nAnsr J released his first single \"School Uniform is not fashion\"<ref>{{Citation|title=\u6821\u670d\u4e0d\u6f6e\u3010Mixtape\u8bd5\u542c\u3011 - AnsrJ|url=https://streetvoice.com/answerj/songs/74248/|language=zh-Hant|access-date=2020-04-04}}</ref> (\u6821\u670d\u4e0d\u6f6e) as early as 2009, when he was a high school student. Taking the school uniform as the topic, although the content is not related to the school uniform, it is enough to attract people to listen to it.\u00a0 This single has a great influence in the local student circle in Chengdu. Every student has this song in the MP3, which can be said to be the youth of many people. Later in 2013, Ansr J focused more on running his own clothing brand Johnny Designs, and music was left behind. In 2016, the single \"Renmin South Road\"(\u4eba\u6c11\u5357\u8def)<ref name=\"163com /> was released, and it is another popular song after \"School Uniform is not fashion\". Then many classic singles and Mixtape \"FNTE\"<ref name=\"163com /> was released, FNTE's full spell is \"from nothing to everything\", from nothing to everything , AnsrJ did indeed rely on himself from scratch, step by step to the present.\n\nLil Shin is also the \"old guy\" of Chengdu Rap House, one of the founding members of C.D.C. As early as the end of BigZoo in 2010, Chengdu Rap entered the Cypher in the C.D.C era, and there was Lil Shin. Lil Shin\u2019s current job is as a director, and he also commutes from 9 to 5 while doing rap. The director's work also made him handy in MV editing, which is also a special skill that other Rapper does not have. One of the Lil Shin's most widely circulated works is \"Intoo\"<ref name=\"163com /> included in \"No. 901\",<ref name=\"163com /> which is a gentle and delicate love song that favors popular style. This song is adapted from [[Sam Smith]]'s classic single \"I'm Not The Only One<ref>{{Citation|title=I'm Not The Only One|url=https://open.spotify.com/track/7795WJLVKJoAyVoOtCWqXN|language=en|access-date=2020-04-04}}</ref>\", which uses the original song as a hook part, and adds a low rap, and illustrates Chengdu dialect is not only suitable for trap, it is also very tender to sing love songs.\n\nAnother member, Mengzi, was also one of the earliest members of the Chengdu rap club. In 2011, he formed the Onstyle combination with Lil Shin, which is also the first combination of the rap club. But Onstyle currently does not have many songs on the platform. Mengzi left the team for almost two years for some reasons and was unable to participate in the team's song.\n\n==Group Members==\nThese are Chinese names; surnames appear first.\n\n* Ansr J\uff08\u5218\u9759\u5b81\uff09from Chengdu\n* Lil Shin\uff08\u674e\u5c14\u65b0\uff09from Chengdu\n* Mengzi\uff08\u5b5f\u5b50\uff09from Chengdu\n\n==Discography==\n'''First album: Ding ji Wan Jia (\u9876\u7ea7\u73a9\u5bb6)'''<ref name=\"163com />\n\nThe group released the first album: Ding Ji Wan Jia in 2018. It consists 12 tracks and one bonus track called \"Food & Liquor\"<ref name=\"163com /> which were made by themselves including lyrics, composing, recording and mixing.\n\n'''Second album: 1Fan!LP (\u4e00\u756a!LP)'''<ref name=\"163com />\n\nIn the same year, they dropped their second album: 1Fan!LP, compared to the last album, the track has increased to 13. In terms of creation, the top three players have made new breakthroughs. The genre is wider than the first album. Here, \"1fan!\" is regarded as top-level meaning, and can also be read as \"Awesome!\"\n\n'''The latest album: Hi Business (\u55e8\u751f\u610f)'''<ref name=\"163com />\n\nThis album contains eight newly created songs, which can be said to be a hard and soft album. In addition to new trap, electronic and rock, there are soft love songs and R&B parts. The single \"Hi business\" pays homage to [[Run-DMC]]. This single is full of skills and strong rhythms; \"Get it done\"<ref name=\"163com /> is the most breakthrough single. In this single, Ansrj combines rock's energy and the powerful rap which is perfectly embodies the top player spirit of A.T.M.; the single \"color\",<ref name=\"163com /> produced by producer G23, is a typical new trap. In the song, Mengzi's flow is quite prominent, which can be called textbook level flow. It is worth mentioning that the single \"friends\",<ref name=\"163com /> in which the comfortable melody of Lil shin shows the all-around rap talent of A.T.M.\n\nA.T.M., who just finished touring in 2019, released the album at the end of the year, and will continue to release their second official album next year. The changeable music style and breakthrough of have laid an all-around stage for them and laid a perfect foundation for their debut next year.\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n\n\n[[Category:Chinese hip hop musicians]]\n", "name_user": "G\u00fcnniX", "label": "safe", "comment": "ref name", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A1_Top_Masta"