ung Medien|language=German|format=ASP|url=http://austriancharts.at/showitem.asp?interpret=The+Beatles&titel=Let+It+Be&cat=a|accessdate=12 October 2012}}</ref>\n|52\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|Belgian Albums Chart (Flanders)<ref name=\"beVlchart\">{{cite web|title= ultratop.be The Beatles \u2013 Let It Be|url=http://www.ultratop.be/nl/showitem.asp?interpret=The+Beatles&titel=Let+It+Be&cat=a|language=Dutch|publisher=Ultratop|work=Hung Medien|format=ASP|accessdate=12 October 2012}}</ref>\n|37\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[Ultratop|Belgian Albums Chart (Wallonia)]]<ref name=\"bewachart\">{{cite web|title= ultratop.be The Beatles \u2013 Let It Be|url=http://www.ultratop.be/fr/showitem.asp?interpret=The+Beatles&titel=Let+It+Be&cat=a|language=Dutch|work= Hung Medien|format=ASP|publisher=Ultratop|accessdate=12 October 2012}}</ref>\n|64\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|Danish Albums Chart<ref name=\"dkchart\">{{cite web|title=danishcharts.com The Beatles \u2013 Let It Be|work=danishcharts.com|url=http://danishcharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=The+Beatles&titel=Let+It+Be&cat=a|format=ASP|accessdate=12 October 2012}}</ref>\n|40\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|Finnish Albums Chart<ref name=\"fichart\">{{cite web|title=finnishcharts.com The Beatles \u2013 Let It Be|url=http://finnishcharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=The+Beatles&titel=Let+It+Be&cat=a|\nwork=Hung Medien|format=ASP|accessdate=12 October 2012}}</ref>\n|34\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|Japanese Albums Chart<ref name=\"Jachart2\">{{cite web| url=http://www.oricon.co.jp/music/release/d/819908/1 | title= Highest position and charting weeks of ''Let It Be'' (2009 Remaster) by The Beatles| language=Japanese| work=oricon.co.jp| publisher=[[Oricon|Oricon Style]] | accessdate=12 October 2012}}</ref>\n|18\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[Top 100 Mexico|Mexican Albums Chart]]<ref name=\"mxchart\">{{cite web|title=mexicancharts.com The Beatles \u2013 Let It Be|publisher=mexicancharts.com|url=http://mexicancharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=The+Beatles&titel=Let+It+Be&cat=a|accessdate