ley|Tony Leadley]] (born 1928), rowed for [[University of Cambridge|Cambridge]] in the 1953 [[The Boat Race|Boat Race]]<ref name=\"Underwood 2010\"/>\n* [[Arthur Coomb|Arthur Grenfell Coomb]] (born 1929), [[Cricket]]er<ref name=\"Underwood 1981\"/>\n* [[Dickie Jeeps]] [[Order of the British Empire|CBE]] (1930-2016), [[Captain (sports)|Captained]] the [[England national rugby union team|England Rugby Team]] and the [[British and Irish Lions|British Lions]]<ref name=\"Underwood 2010\"/>\n* [[Bob Gale (cricketer)|Bob Gale]] (1933\u20132018), Middlesex [[Cricket]]er<ref name=\"Underwood 2010\"/>\n* [[Geoff Millman]] (1934\u20132005), [[England cricket team|England]] [[Cricket]]er<ref name=\"Underwood 2010\"/>\n* [[Graham Jarrett]] (1937\u20132004), [[Cricket]]er<ref name=\"Underwood 2010\"/>\n* [[Peter Watts (cricketer, born 1938)|Peter David Watts]] (born 1938), [[Cricket]]er<ref name=\"Underwood 2010\"/>\n* [[Hamilton Milton|Hamilton (\"Tony\") Pierre Matt Milton]] (born 1938), swimmer at the [[1960 Summer Olympics]]<ref name=\"Underwood 2010\"/>\n* [[Peter Kippax]] (1940\u20132017), [[first-class cricket|Cricketer]]<ref name=\"Underwood 2010\"/>\n* [[Andrew David Curtis|Andrew Curtis]] (born 1943), [[Cricket]]er<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.espncricinfo.com/england/content/player/11499.html|title=Andrew Curtis|website=Cricinfo|accessdate=30 June 2019}}</ref>\n* [[Lionel Edward Weston]] (born 1947), [[England national rugby union team|England]] [[Rugby union|Rugby]] International<ref name=\"Underwood 2010\"/>\n* [[Peter Knapp]] (born 1949), [[Rowing (sport)|rower]] who competed in the [[Rowing at the 1968 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's eight|1968 Summer Olympics]]<ref name=\"Underwood 2010\"/>\n* [[John Yallop]] (born 1949), [[Rowing (sport)|rower]] who won a Silver Medal at the [[1976 Summer Olympics]] in Montreal<ref name=\"Underwood 2010\"/>\n* [[Neil Keron]] (born 1953), [[Rowing (sport)|rower]] who competed in the [[1976 Summer Olympics]]<ref name=\"Underwood 2010